        "timestamp": "2018-03-22 12:23:57.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nWait a minute, isn't it supposed to be sending 202 responses? Isn't that what the loop is needed for? And then return whether 200 or 4xx failed? Or is that functionality already in there?",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
